unifiedshield (1.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * Initial release.
  - Multi-core support: Xray, NaïveProxy, Hysteria2, TUIC
  - DPI detection with automatic core switching (threshold > 0.72)
  - Split tunnel: Iranian IPs excluded for local service access
  - Kill switch: always-on VPN lockdown mode
  - DNS: Alibaba/Tencent primary (Cloudflare blocked in Iran)
  - OTA updates via GitHub Releases with SHA256 verification
  - No root required (uses CAP_NET_ADMIN capability)
  - systemd integration with watchdog support

 -- UnifiedShield Team <team@unifiedshield.org>  Mon, 01 Jan 2024 00:00:00 +0000
